speak our language?! How?

222
00:14:09,042 --> 00:14:11,877
It doesn't matter. Just do as I say. Hide!

223
00:14:11,944 --> 00:14:14,719
- Hide or they will kill you.
- You are one of us!

224
00:14:16,683 --> 00:14:18,116
