225
00:14:18,184 --> 00:14:20,052
<i>Bishop Swithern: Then I will tell you this:</i>

226
00:14:20,119 --> 00:14:22,220
One day, you will be caught.

227
00:14:22,288 --> 00:14:24,455
<i>We will catch you and crucify you... </i>

228
00:14:24,523 --> 00:14:27,159
<i>for an apostate is the lowest
and the vilest of all creatures</i>

229
