554
00:35:38,379 --> 00:35:40,313
(Running footfalls)

555
00:35:43,317 --> 00:35:45,285
(Barrels clatter)

556
00:35:50,390 --> 00:35:52,825
(Water churns)

557
00:35:59,872 --> 00:36:02,474
Siggy: This way! To the mountains.

558
00:36:02,542 --> 00:36:04,243
Hurry! Go, Hvitserk.

559
00:36:04,311 --> 00:36:06,078
